<section class="lib-section" id="animations">
    <div class="lib-section-title">✨ Animations</div>
    <div class="lib-section-desc">
        Classes from <code>_animations.css</code>. Three categories: <strong
            >Loop</strong
        > (always-on), <strong>Hover-triggered</strong> (CSS :hover), <strong
            >Scroll-triggered</strong
        > (IntersectionObserver via <code>njx.js</code>). Combine with <code
            >.anim-fast</code
        >, <code>.anim-slow</code>, <code>.anim-delay-*</code> modifiers.
    </div>

    <!-- ── Sub-section: Loop ── -->
    <div class="lib-subsection-title">
        <span>Loop — always-on</span>
        <span class="lib-subsection-desc"
            >No JS needed. These run continuously as long as the class is
            applied.</span
        >
    </div>

